name: StreamPal
0:
”Alexa, ask Stream Pal when the last episode of True Detective aired?”
”Alexa, ask Stream Pal when did the current episode of The Expanse come out?”
”Alexa, ask Stream Pal about the last episode of Game of Thrones.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: stream pal
des:
Do you know the feeling? 
You're standing in the kitchen, preparing your dinner and your partner comes in to ask what you're watching tonight. You're wondering if the new episode of this TV series you're both watching came out already, so you take to Alexa to find out.

Ask StreamPal when the last/current/recent episode of your favorite TV series came out. Fingers crossed it's today 🤞
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
